"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"在ETH layer2的跨链协议交互的时候，可能会用到XDAI主网币。比如Hop协议和connext协议，XDAI的手续费是很低的，但是为了搞一点XDAI主网币，竟然费了老大鼻子劲了，真是想不到啊......下面是wx群友提供的办法，亲测可用，首先BSC链上的DAI可以通过各种办法获得，执行后面两步跨链网关就可以了。\\n\\n如何从bsc上把dai提到xdai网络并换成xdai：\\n1、薄饼买dai\\n2、<https://omni.xdaichain.com/bridge> 跨链把dai跨到xdai网络变成bdai\\n3、<https://app.honeyswap.org/#/swap> 把bdai换成xdai\",\"timestamp\":1635844398,\"title\":\"如何从bsc上把dai提到xdai网络并换成xdai\"},\"digest\":\"1CamvisDewHpitLSIgpvXZByamW-iW1ZjPkAGJYFAeA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xd0874a9112C969056Ca974bD58aF892d977c9dD9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hSjwIt9zVus0E-trUouu6HCn28QSGReoNzHsxw_A0o0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"bNeQYSEUvdiLBCqchz0lPSwDw4U6F4hMGXGQm_wSqLI\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"s8Gq8PjMrpaDlZk8FGXixSA3n38RaWN4qGmboCxteC_CmpIECIvHSaSSYI1jD29f1SuDb1GlWHWmR35xFXXS6Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x441834143ac659c7420a9fd4e521ba158561edd30dd1af15a05455b29dfaab5b5a7c532127784afd311ea4707210dbe6eb7bd590ff6bc5ea1ead0274acbcd8681c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hSjwIt9zVus0E-trUouu6HCn28QSGReoNzHsxw_A0o0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"bNeQYSEUvdiLBCqchz0lPSwDw4U6F4hMGXGQm_wSqLI\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"1CamvisDewHpitLSIgpvXZByamW-iW1ZjPkAGJYFAeA\"}"